articles.title: Lovlina Borgohain helps India wrap World Boxing Championship with four golds - Hindustan Times
articles.description: The Tokyo Olympic bronze medallist produced a strong show in the 70-75kg finals, where she defeated Australia's Caitlin Anne Parker with 5-2 split decision win.
